General.Name: Wellard Ltd
General.Description: Wellard Limited supplies livestock vessels and livestock in Australia and internationally. It operates through Chartering and Other segments. The company engages in the livestock transportation, which include the carriage of cargo owned by third parties through its vessels; livestock marketing business; and buying livestock from various sources for export to buyers in international markets. Wellard Limited was founded in 1950 and is headquartered in Fremantle, Australia.
